description: Ditch your go-to fried rice with this flavour-packed recipe topped with juicy prawn dumplings.
name: Prawn Dumplings With Vegetable Fried Rice Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large nonstick frying pan over medium-high heat. Add corn and garlic. Cook, stirring, for 3 minutes or until golden brown. Add broccoli and carrot. Cook, stirring, for 2 minutes. Add rice and cook, stirring, for a further 2 minutes or until heated and vegetables are tender. Add onion. Remove from heat.
Meanwhile, cook dumplings, in batches, in a large saucepan of boiling water for 2 minutes or until they float to the surface. Drain.
Spoon rice into shallow bowls. Top with dumplings. Sprinkle with chilli. Serve with soy sauce.
